dataset_id: NPP Tropical Forest: Manaus, Brazil, 1963-1990 , R1
title: NPP Tropical Forest: Manaus, Brazil, 1963-1990 , R1
summary: This data set includes six ASCII files (.txt format). Five files contain productivity values for several types of tropical Amazon rainforest near Manaus, Brazil studied between 1963 and 1990, and one file contains monthly and annual climate data for the period 1910-1993.
